headline: Lennar Unveils River Bridge Ranch in San Marcos, TX
summary: Lennar, one of the nation's leading homebuilders, is now selling at River Bridge Ranch, a premier community of single-family homes in San Marcos, Texas. Ideally located near downtown San Marcos, River Bridge Ranch offers a selection of 28 single-family home designs and ample lifestyle amenities that San Marcos homeowners have long desired.

headline: Warren Buffett plowed more than $1 billion into three stocks, and it says a lot about where he sees consumers’ priorities right now: Houses, beer, and gas
summary: Berkshire Hathaway's 2025 investments focus on consumer-driven brands like Lennar, Chevron, and Constellation.
